Save a Recipe
You have two options when saving a recipe:
Save Recipe—Save the recipe with its current name.
Save As New...—Save a copy of your recipe with a new name.

Open a saved recipe on the Dataflows & Recipes tab to update it or run it. See Manage Recipes.
